data.description: Centrally located, but quiet and private.  Excellent home for in-laws or second family.Circular Driveway,  PRIVATE COURTYARD, 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, southwest style home, with a New 1892 sf  detached very private Casita with 2 large bedrooms and bathrooms, living room and full kitchen. (Total of 5 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms)  Casita also has two large garages w EV chargers. Resort like  backyard with Gorgeous Natural ROCK WATERFALL and sparkling heated POOL! BUILT IN BBQ., freshly painted interior 2021, New bedroom flooring 2021, Stack Stone 2-way GAS FIREPLACE, . The main kitchen features a granite countertop & SS appliances.  The Casita has a modern large white cabinet kitchen and quartz counters.  Massive private back yards for tennis or pickle ball.  RV Parking.  No HOA Easy to show.
